Further information
This growing and prestigious global insurance business is seeking to hire a Deputy Chief Actuary to work on a regional basis and lead a small team in the Singapore office.
The role will be varied and include an interesting and challenging mix of pricing, reserving and capital modelling duties but also with a strong theme of strategic projects and business planning activities.
If you class yourself a technically strong and dynamic non-life actuary who is seeking a step up in your career then my client wants to hear from you!
A willingness to travel is essential as well as being a fully qualified actuary, combined with superb communication skills.
